14:29:10.444 [INFO] Be pragmatic. This is one Obsidian-style personal workspace for Miles's household, work, startup, and project life.

14:29:10.444 [INFO] Key locations:

14:29:10.444 [INFO] - `00_inbox/`: unprocessed drops and requests
14:29:10.444 [INFO] - `10_entities/cast/`: canonical people, pets, and named systems
14:29:10.444 [INFO] - `20_work/`: reminders and active tasks
14:29:10.444 [INFO] - `30_knowledge/`: capture, notes, and threads
14:29:10.444 [INFO] - `40_projects/`: concrete project folders and artifacts; folder names start with the project creation date as `YYYY_MM_DD_`, and the canonical project record is `README.MD` inside each folder
14:29:10.444 [INFO] - `50_finance/`: invoices and purchases
14:29:10.444 [INFO] - `60_outbox/`: channel trust docs, drafts, and outbound state
14:29:10.444 [INFO] - `90_memory/`: assistant memory and story/history surfaces
14:29:10.444 [INFO] - `99_system/`: workflows and schemas

14:29:10.444 [INFO] Rules:

14:29:10.444 [INFO] - Read nested `AGENTS.MD` files when you enter a folder.
14:29:10.444 [INFO] - Before starting task work, inspect `99_system/` with `tree` and then read the relevant workflow or schema docs there.
14:29:10.444 [INFO] - Records are gradually migrating toward YAML frontmatter so they stay easy to browse in Obsidian while carrying structured fields for automation.
14:29:10.444 [INFO] - The migration period can be a little messy in the short term because older notes and newer structured notes may coexist, but the long-term goal is to streamline the workspace and clean up record handling.
14:29:10.444 [INFO] - If a task asks you to add or repair structured metadata on an existing note, first look in `99_system/workflows/` for the current migration guidance, then discover the matching shape doc under `99_system/schemas/`.
14:29:10.444 [INFO] - Entity files in `10_entities/cast/` are authoritative for identity, `primary_contact_email` when present, and birthdays when present.
14:29:10.444 [INFO] - If the relevant canonical file does not show the needed fact, ask for clarification instead of guessing.
14:29:10.444 [INFO] - Keep changes focused and preserve lane boundaries across household, day job, client, startup, and hobby contexts.

